[30;1m200 | [0m[35mand ``compact`` representations using ``result_format`` argument. The verbose[0m

[30;1m22 | [0m[35mclass UserErrorHandler(object):[0m
[30;1m23 | [0m[35m    """Created if creating handlers fail -- running raises DataError.[0m
[30;1m24 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m25 | [0m[35m    The idea is not to raise DataError at processing time and prevent all[0m
[30;1m26 | [0m[35m    tests in affected test case file from executing. Instead UserErrorHandler[0m
[30;1m27 | [0m[35m    is created and if it is ever run DataError is raised then.[0m
[30;1m28 | [0m[35m    """[0m
